title: Anthony Lucero from Cult Leader

description:
Episode 228 - There’s heavy and then there’s Cult Leader. I love this band and you should as well. I had to have Anthony Lucero, vocalist of the band, on the show and we did it! In our lengthy discussion we spoke of his experience with Salt Lake City, the influence of religion and subculture. A real insightful chat, so please enjoy! Get 3 free meals on me!
